00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:08,520
To eat a cup of instant noodles

594
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:12,240
and drink a cup of milk tea.

595
00:23:12,840 --> 00:23:13,400
I think it's totally worth it.

596
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:14,680
After I was diagnosed with dilated cardiomyopathy,

597
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,520
I understood even more

598
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:18,920
why my dad

599
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:21,720
loved photography so much when he was alive,

600
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:23,040
and why he put so much effort

601
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:25,120
into caring for his flowers.

602
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:26,760
Because when a person's life

603
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:29,560
is counting down, they'll...

604
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:30,400
What do you mean, counting down?

605
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:31,280
Who are you looking down on?

606
00:23:31,800 --> 00:23:32,800
With a whole family of doctors,

607
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,480
you think we can't protect

608
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:36,080
a brat like you?

609
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:36,800
I just mean maybe.

610
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:37,680
So, Sister Xiaoran,

611
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:39,920
don't worry too much.

612
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,680
That child will definitely be like me,

613
00:23:41,800 --> 00:23:42,840
born with love

614
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,520
and anticipation.

615
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:45,480
Simply put, in this surgery,

616
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,360
we make a minimally invasive puncture

617
00:23:50,520 --> 00:23:51,840
from outside your abdomen

618
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:53,160
and go all the way

619
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:55,000
into the baby's heart.

620
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:57,000
Then we'll use

621
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:58,520
a very small balloon

622
00:23:58,520 --> 00:23:59,720
to gently open

623
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,240
the blocked door

624
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,240
inside the baby's heart,

625
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:03,480
so blood can flow through.

626
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:04,760
Her heart function

627
00:24:05,080 --> 00:24:05,800
can then improve.

628
00:24:05,800 --> 00:24:06,800
Professor Fang, who will lead the surgery,

629
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,360
is an authority in this field.

630
00:24:09,520 --> 00:24:10,720
She has extensive experience.

631
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:12,400
But at the same time,

632
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:13,400
this surgery

633
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:15,080
is extremely difficult.

634
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:16,120
Especially since you're carrying twins,

635
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:19,000
that makes the situation

636
00:24:19,280 --> 00:24:19,840
even more complicated.

637
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:21,000
If the surgery doesn't go well,

638
00:24:21,840 --> 00:24:23,720
it could bring great risks

639
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,080
to you

640
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:26,480
and both babies.

641
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:28,120
Do you all understand?

642
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:31,080
Think carefully before deciding.

643
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,560
I've made up my mind.

644
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:37,200
Do you have any other questions?

645
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,600
Director Zhou,

646
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:45,920
I heard

647
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:47,360
Professor Fang is your mother. Is that true?

648
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,360
Yes.

649
00:24:51,120 --> 00:24:51,480
Director,

650
00:24:53,520 --> 00:24:53,880
you've done everything you can

651
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:55,600
to help us get funding,

652
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:57,680
and brought all of us

653
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,000
from so far away

654
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:00,080
to Dongjiang.

655
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,040
You don't just want to help me have surgery,

656
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:03,200
you've also tried everything

657
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,520
to save me and my babies.

658
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:05,800
I trust you.

659
00:25:06,520 --> 00:25:07,560
And I trust Professor Fang.

660
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:09,760
We know very well

661
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:13,400
who is truly good to us.

662
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:15,000
So

663
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:17,560
no matter what happens,

664
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:20,000
don't worry.

665
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,000
We will absolutely not

666
00:25:21,360 --> 00:25:22,560
blame anyone.

667
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:23,720
We will do everything we can.

668
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:29,000
Why not reduce one fetus?

669
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:46,800
Why insist on intrauterine intervention?

670
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,160
Xuemei is very determined.

671
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:50,280
And there is still a chance worth fighting for.

672
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:52,160
Fight how? Who's fighting?

673
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:53,560
Easy for you to say.

674
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:54,600
Professor Fang.

675
00:25:55,800 --> 00:25:56,480
You found her?

676
00:25:58,280 --> 00:25:58,840
Now we're just waiting

677
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,080
for the balloon barcode approval.

678
00:26:01,080 --> 00:26:01,680
You should've said so earlier.

679
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:04,080
If Professor Fang is coming,

680
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:05,120
then that's not a gamble.

681
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:06,280
That's a showcase.

682
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:07,720
When is the surgery scheduled?

683
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:08,480
Next Tuesday.

684
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,200
I'm going to a meeting this Friday.

685
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:11,720
On Tuesday,

686
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,240
I should be able to perform well

687
00:26:13,280 --> 00:26:14,160
in front of Professor Fang.

688
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,200
Where are you going now?

689
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,000
To a heart transplant forum.

690
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:18,160
By the way,

691
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:19,800
the surgery time

692
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:21,000
for the congenital heart disease case in Guizhou

693
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,120
has been set.

694
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:22,840
It's next week.

695
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:23,480
Okay.

696
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:24,400
I'll follow your arrangement.

697
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:27,800
Dinner tonight?

698
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:29,680
Who's having dinner with you?

699
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:30,800
Tonight

700
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:32,400
is movie night for me and Xiaoran.

701
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:33,480
Eat by yourself.

702
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:36,480
Lonely man.

703
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:41,680
Lonely Director Zhou.

704
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,440
Boss Rui did well today.

705
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:47,160
He said for Sunday family day,

706
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:47,920
he'll treat us.

707
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:50,040
Then let's mark that down.

708
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,160
Next family day,

709
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,360
we'll really make him pay.

710
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,160
What time exactly

711
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,160
is your flight tomorrow?

712
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,040
Eight in the morning to Nanjing.

713
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,560
That early?

714
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:07,600
Then why don't we skip tonight?

715
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:09,440
No skipping.

716
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,360
We agreed on movie night.

717
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,120
It's not easy for both of us

718
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:12,680
to be off duty.

719
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,480
We must watch the movie.

720
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,240
The same one?

721
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:17,840
Yes.

722
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:20,600
Didn't we not finish it last time?

723
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:21,400
Here.

724
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:24,360
Come on.

725
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:27,280
Fast-forward to where we left off.

726
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,480
They said the best part

727
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:30,200
of this movie is the drawing scene.

728
00:27:30,360 --> 00:27:31,600
Who told you that?

729
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,400
I saw it in short videos.

730
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:08,680
It's biting my hand.

731
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:11,160
Did they draw yet?

732
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,720
Go to sleep.

733
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,720
We'll watch the drawing next time.

734
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,120
You're not watching anymore?

735
00:28:25,760 --> 00:28:26,360
How did you fall asleep?

736
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:45,160
Good night.

737
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:48,040
Sis.

738
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:05,560
Have you really thought this through?

739
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,400
I don't want to wear these socks anymore.

740
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,280
Help me change into that pair.

741
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:30,480
Look.

742
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:56,480
They're pretty cute.

743
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,000
Do they look good?

744
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:08,160
They do.

745
00:30:08,760 --> 00:30:09,800
Obstetrics, anesthesiology, neonatology—

746
00:30:10,720 --> 00:30:12,800
I've coordinated with all of them.

747
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,280
If you need the hospital

748
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,280
to provide any other assistance later,

749
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:16,520
tell me anytime.

750
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:19,600
I'll fully support you.

751
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:21,480
Now we're just waiting for the balloon approval.

752
00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:23,400
Once it comes through, we'll operate.

753
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,720
This will be the first case in China

754
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,720
of intrauterine intervention on twins.

755
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:28,760
I'm looking forward to all of you

756
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,040
completing it beautifully.

757
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:31,680
We'll do our best.

758
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,080
By the way,

759
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:35,600
a few days ago,

760
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:37,480
I attended a Health Commission meeting.

761
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:39,040
The leaders specifically mentioned

762
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:41,480
strengthening Dongjiang's

763
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,360
medical support

764
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:45,120
for remote areas.

765
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,280
They especially mentioned

766
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:47,600
the congenital heart disease patients

767
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:50,440
Xiaofeng brought back this time.

768
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,200
They're paying close attention.

769
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:53,160
So after this first group of patients

770
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,680
is successfully treated,

771
00:30:54,840 --> 00:30:55,800
this project

772
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:56,880
can actually be used as a model

773
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:58,400
for promotion

774
00:30:59,360 --> 00:31:00,360
and publicity.

775
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:01,440
That's wonderful.

776
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:02,800
Xiaofeng has trained in Guizhou

777
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:05,160
these past few years,

778
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:06,120
and he's changed a lot.

779
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:07,160
Whether in a doctor's

780
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,680
vision

781
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:11,240
or perspective,

782
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:12,800
he has made great progress.

783
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:13,800
Thank you for supporting him all these years.

784
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:16,560
Senior sister,

785
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:19,600
you're too kind.

786
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,080
Actually,

787
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:25,160
Xiaofeng himself

788
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:27,520
has worked very hard.

789
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:30,800
Maybe

790
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:32,000
you've also heard

791
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:34,240
that I'll be transferred soon.

792
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:35,680
Before I leave,

793
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:37,440
one of the things

794
00:31:37,560 --> 00:31:38,560
I most want to do well

795
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,160
is to find cardiology

796
00:31:42,560 --> 00:31:43,200
the best possible

797
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:44,680
department leader.

798
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,280
Xiaofeng, comparatively speaking,

799
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:47,520
is young

800
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:48,760
and less senior.

801
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:50,120
But his strengths are

802
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:52,600
an excellent record,

803
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:53,800
solid clinical skills,

804
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,800
and a grounded character.

805
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:57,800
Especially

806
00:31:58,280 --> 00:32:00,760
in the past two years,

807
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:01,720
his work in Guizhou

808
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:05,080
has been outstanding.

809
00:32:05,080 --> 00:32:05,600
So

810
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:06,800
you could say

811
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:07,880
he has both strengths and weaknesses.

812
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,400
No matter how the recruitment turns out,

813
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:12,200
I think he can

814
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:13,480
walk his own path well.

815
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,160
I know this period

816
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,480
is quite sensitive,

817
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:19,600
and I should avoid suspicion.

818
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:21,480
But I happened to be here

819
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,480
for Xuemei's pre-op exam,

820
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:28,360
so I came to see you.

821
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,920
Wonderful.

822
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,080
Come, have some tea.

823
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:32,920
Professor Fang.

824
00:32:33,520 --> 00:32:34,440
Sorry to keep you waiting.

825
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:35,240
Your Americano.

826
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:37,680
Thank you.

827
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:38,920
I just got here too.

828
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,200
I haven't waited long.

829
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:41,160
I asked to meet you

830
00:32:41,360 --> 00:32:42,800
mainly to tell you

831
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:43,720
that I'm pushing forward

832
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,800
the procedures for the mini balloon.

833
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,160
I also called this morning.

834
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:48,080
The barcode

835
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:49,440
should be finalized

836
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:50,880
in about three days.

837
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:52,480
Good. Thank you for your hard work.

838
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,360
Actually, for this matter,

839
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,920
a phone call would have been enough.

840
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,720
You didn't need to come all this way.

841
00:32:56,840 --> 00:32:58,440
It's my job.

842
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:00,880
Since you chose our product,

843
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:02,520
I'll definitely do my best

844
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:04,800
to get everything ready.

845
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,800
There's one thing

846
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:09,840
I want to make clear.

847
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,000
I chose your product

848
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:12,600
out of professional need. It's official business.

849
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:16,360
If personal ties get mixed in,

850
00:33:17,040 --> 00:33:17,800
this circle is small,

851
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:19,160
and things may become complicated.

852
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:20,800
I understand what you mean.

853
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:21,920
Don't worry.

854
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:22,920
Director Zhou and I

855
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:24,240
are simply schoolmates.

856
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,240
When we were together before,

857
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:27,600
we weren't very public either.

858
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:29,920
You know

859
00:33:30,120 --> 00:33:31,160
he doesn't like drawing attention.

860
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,440
After all these years,

861
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:34,360
very few people in the field

862
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,880
know about it anymore.

863
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:39,440
And we don't really have much contact now.

864
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:41,360
Speaking of our school days,

865
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:43,080
back then,

866
00:33:43,360 --> 00:33:44,480
you weren't only my teacher,

867
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:46,760
but also an elder to me,

868
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:47,760
and even my idol.

869
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,560
I'm very happy

870
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:49,720
to cross paths with you professionally this time.

871
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,160
And

872
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:52,600
I really admire you.

873
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,440
Your courage and boldness—

874
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,400
if the twin intrauterine intervention succeeds,

875
00:33:55,800 --> 00:33:57,280
you'll absolutely outshine

876
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,360
all peers at home and abroad.

877
00:34:00,840 --> 00:34:01,720
As doctors,

878
00:34:01,840 --> 00:34:03,040
we always hope

879
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:04,720
to keep improving

880
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:05,720
our skills.

881
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:07,440
Yes.

882
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,680
Without your mini balloon,

883
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,440
I wouldn't dare attempt

884
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,360
such a complicated intervention.

885
00:34:12,560 --> 00:34:13,800
Even the most advanced product

886
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,880
requires superb technique

887
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:16,080
to be used properly.

888
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:17,000
So I think

